# Outputs Directory

This directory will contain the generated output files from your survival analysis.

## Required Outputs

Your analysis should generate these 3 files:

### Kaplan-Meier Analysis
- `km_survival_plot.png` - Survival curves comparing groups

### Cox Proportional Hazards
- `cox_summary.csv` - Regression coefficients, hazard ratios, p-values

### Random Survival Forest
- `rsf_importance.png` - Feature importance bar chart

## File Formats

### CSV Files
```csv
covariate,coef,exp(coef),se(coef),z,p,lower 95%,upper 95%
age,0.023,1.023,0.011,2.09,0.037,1.001,1.046
stage_III,0.567,1.763,0.234,2.42,0.015,1.114,2.791
...
```

## .gitkeep

This file exists to keep the empty `outputs/` directory in git.
You can delete this README after generating your outputs.
